# ğŸ“Œ Network Topologies  

## 1ï¸âƒ£ **Bus Topology**  
âœ” All devices connected to a **single central cable**.  

[Device1]----[Device2]----[Device3]----[Device4]


2ï¸âƒ£ Ring Topology
âœ” Devices connected in a circular structure.
       [Device1] ---- [Device2]
          |              |
       [Device4] ---- [Device3]

3ï¸âƒ£ Star Topology
âœ” Devices connected to a central hub/switch.

          [Device1]  
             |  
[Device2] -- [Hub] -- [Device3]  
             |  
          [Device4]  

4ï¸âƒ£ Tree Topology (Bus + Star)
âœ” Hierarchical structure combining Bus & Star topologies.

          [Root Hub]  
          /    |    \  
      [Hub1] [Hub2] [Hub3]  
      /   \     |      |  
 [D1]   [D2]  [D3]   [D4]  

5ï¸âƒ£ Mesh Topology
âœ” Every device connects to every other device.

       [D1] ----- [D2]
        |  \      /  |
        |   \    /   |
       [D3] ----- [D4]
